
COMMAND:
   dead 

ART:
   Dead is a very useful skill. It allows a monk to act dead.
   A sucessful irritated victim will then stop the fight.
   After all if the victim stops the attack depends on your
   and the victims intelligence. 

POWER:
    intelligence/skilldependend 

INFO:
  Dead is only useful when it's practiced on a very high level.
  This skill is 'very hard' to advance by training without master. 

PS:
  The victim will learn from your acting dead, depending on her int.
  So any try will lower the change of success.
